---
import { profile } from '../data/profile';
---

<section id="summary" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Summary</h2>

    <div class="summary-content">
      <p>
        I'm a software engineer focused on building fast, scalable web and mobile products
        with clean code and solid UX. With 6+ years in the industry, I've worked on large-scale
        products, white-label platforms, and high-traffic applications.
      </p>

      <p>
        What I enjoy the most: turning complex requirements into simple interfaces,
        performance, architecture, and maintainable code, building frontend systems
        that grow with the product.
      </p>

      <p>
        Beyond coding, I mentor developers, review code, conduct interviews,
        and help teams grow through better engineering practices.
      </p>

      <blockquote>
        I build products that scale, from architecture to production.
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .summary-content {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .summary-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .summary-content blockquote {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding-left: 2rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .summary-content blockquote {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
